-- Greece can achieve its austerity goals: Merkel
-- 
-- Mon Mar 1, 2010 11:52am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/03/01/us-eurozone-germany-austerity-idUSTRE6203I320100301

 

 HANOVER, Germany  (Reuters) - German Chancellor Angela Merkel said on Monday she believes Greece can fulfill its budget consolidation targets and that those steps are the best way to stop or minimize speculation against the euro. 

 She was speaking at a joint news conference with Spanish Prime Minister Jose Luis Rodriguez Zapatero. (Reporting by  Erik Kirschbaum )